107
00:07:34.143 --> 00:07:35.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets...</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:35.902 --> 00:07:37.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>they were here.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:37.782 --> 00:07:39.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They spoke to me.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:39.142 --> 00:07:41.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You had a vision, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We saw nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:41.780 --> 00:07:42.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did they say?</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:42.780 --> 00:07:44.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They mentioned something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about a Reckoning.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:45.204 --> 00:07:46.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that a part of some prophecy?</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:46.619 --> 00:07:47.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not one that I know of.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:48.179 --> 00:07:49.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's get out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:49.979 --> 00:07:52.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Jake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be leaving soon.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:52.258 --> 00:07:56.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have got to find out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what those inscriptions say.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:57.136 --> 00:07:59.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish we could translate them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more quickly</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:59.215 --> 00:08:01.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we don't have the resources.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:01.335 --> 00:08:03.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fortunately, we do.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:07.653 --> 00:08:11.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a pretty good idea what this was</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the minute I laid eyes on it.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:12.452 --> 00:08:13.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That confirms it.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:14.917 --> 00:08:16.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a slab of stone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with some writing on it.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:16.650 --> 00:08:17.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax...</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:17.969 --> 00:08:20.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want me to say, Benjamin?</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:20.649 --> 00:08:23.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not picking up any</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>residual energy readings--</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:23.289 --> 00:08:26.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>certainly nothing that would explain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how it threw you across the room.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:26.647 --> 00:08:28.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to translate the inscriptions.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:29.886 --> 00:08:31.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was afraid you were going to say that.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:34.507 --> 00:08:36.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Ranjen's translation program.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:36.244 --> 00:08:38.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not complete,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but at least it's a start.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:39.563 --> 00:08:40.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:46.521 --> 00:08:47.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:48.521 --> 00:08:49.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chimes jingling )</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:49.800 --> 00:08:51.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>CLERGYMAN: Services are about to begin.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:58.598 --> 00:09:00.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, services are about to begin.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:05.275 --> 00:09:06.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Ops to Captain Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:06.715 --> 00:09:07.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:07.915 --> 00:09:09.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>We just received</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>a communication from Bajor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:10.743 --> 00:09:12.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kai Winn is on her way to the station.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:27.829 --> 00:09:30.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Welcome to Deep Space Nine, Your Eminence.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:30.468 --> 00:09:31.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:31.908 --> 00:09:33.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What brings you to the station?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:33.547 --> 00:09:35.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should think that would be clear.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:35.986 --> 00:09:39.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You removed an artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from an archaeological site</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:39.106 --> 00:09:40.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>without consulting the Vedek Assembly.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:41.945 --> 00:09:43.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I meant no disrespect.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:43.544 --> 00:09:47.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how we would be sensitive to such matters.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:48.630 --> 00:09:49.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>During the Occupation,</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:49.342 --> 00:09:52.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Cardassians plundered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor's historical treasures</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:52.262 --> 00:09:53.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as if it were their right.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:54.421 --> 00:09:57.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never imagined that you would behave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in such a manner.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:58.206 --> 00:10:00.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assure you that the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be returned</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:00.539 --> 00:10:02.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as soon as I've finished studying it.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:02.458 --> 00:10:05.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was not aware that you had</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>expertise in Bajoran history.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:05.897 --> 00:10:08.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then why not leave the artifact</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:08.817 --> 00:10:10.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the hands of those who do?</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:10.856 --> 00:10:12.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are scholars on Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:12.575 --> 00:10:15.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>who've devoted their lives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the study of such things.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:10:15.734 --> 00:10:18.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand, but I brought it here</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:10:18.374 --> 00:10:20.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because I believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's what the Prophets want.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:10:20.813 --> 00:10:21.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:21.973 --> 00:10:25.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I take it this has something to do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with your vision?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:25.771 --> 00:10:26.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:28.210 --> 00:10:29.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:29.291 --> 00:10:32.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I-I didn't realize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the Prophets told you</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:32.250 --> 00:10:33.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to bring the relic here.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:34.938 --> 00:10:36.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, they didn't... not in so many words.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:36.928 --> 00:10:38.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:38.767 --> 00:10:40.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then exactly what did they say?</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:41.646 --> 00:10:42.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:43.206 --> 00:10:45.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's difficult to explain.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:45.925 --> 00:10:47.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets are not always clear.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:48.325 --> 00:10:50.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, since they have never spoken to me</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:51.523 --> 00:10:53.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to take your word for it.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:54.203 --> 00:10:57.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I know is, for now, it belongs here.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:58.961 --> 00:11:02.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who am I to argue</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Emissary of the Prophets?</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:11:09.238 --> 00:11:13.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And then she contacted Starfleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and lodged a formal protest.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:14.117 --> 00:11:16.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that why Admiral Ross</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted to talk to you?</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:17.236 --> 00:11:18.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, how'd it go?</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:18.756 --> 00:11:21.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He told me to stop meddling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in Bajoran affairs</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:21.394 --> 00:11:23.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and return the damn tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:23.394 --> 00:11:26.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know how Starfleet feels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about this Emissary thing.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:26.633 --> 00:11:29.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It makes them very uncomfortable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've allowed the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:29.473 --> 00:11:31.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to view you as a religious icon.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:32.752 --> 00:11:34.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It used to make you uncomfortable, too.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:35.191 --> 00:11:36.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:37.150 --> 00:11:40.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess the Prophets have spoken to me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one too many times.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:40.749 --> 00:11:43.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember when you used</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to call them "wormhole aliens."</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:43.948 --> 00:11:47.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wormhole aliens or Prophets...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it really doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:47.667 --> 00:11:51.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The fact is, they exist out of time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and over the centuries</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:51.546 --> 00:11:54.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they've given the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>glimpses of the future</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:54.385 --> 00:11:56.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>glimpses that the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have written down</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:56.304 --> 00:11:58.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to help them guide succeeding generations.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:58.184 --> 00:12:02.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If whatever is written here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can help me avoid mistakes</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:03.229 --> 00:12:06.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>can help me make the right decisions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then I'd be a fool to ignore it.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:06.661 --> 00:12:09.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fair enough, but if you don't mind</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:09.260 --> 00:12:12.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to continue to think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of them as wormhole aliens.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:12.739 --> 00:12:14.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I know is...</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:14.899 --> 00:12:17.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that they have a relationship with Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:18.538 --> 00:12:20.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that stretches back over a thousand years.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:20.697 --> 00:12:23.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They care what happens to Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:23.337 --> 00:12:25.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They proved that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when they kept the Dominion fleet</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:25.575 --> 00:12:26.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:26.895 --> 00:12:28.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't you have to talk them into it?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:29.495 --> 00:12:33.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't they say they would exact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some kind of penance for helping you?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:33.333 --> 00:12:35.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, but they listened,</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:12:36.252 --> 00:12:39.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they saved Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the rest of the Alpha Quadrant.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:39.291 --> 00:12:41.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now they're asking me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for something in return.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:12:41.811 --> 00:12:43.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what it is yet</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:12:43.770 --> 00:12:46.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm not going to return</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the tablet until I do.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:12:46.650 --> 00:12:49.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the key. I can feel it.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:12:49.288 --> 00:12:51.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you're wrong about that, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:51.528 --> 00:12:52.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What have you got?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:52.727 --> 00:12:55.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer has translated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>part of the inscription.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:55.167 --> 00:12:57.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It probably lacks the eloquence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the original passage</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:12:57.606 --> 00:12:59.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but you'll get the gist of it.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:00.325 --> 00:13:02.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here it is in modern Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:13:04.244 --> 00:13:06.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: "The time of Reckoning is at hand.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:13:07.683 --> 00:13:09.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"The Prophets will weep.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:13:10.243 --> 00:13:12.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Their sorrow will consume...</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:19.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Gateway to the Temple."</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:13:20.599 --> 00:13:22.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me I'm wrong...</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:13:23.878 --> 00:13:26.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but isn't the Gateway</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Temple Deep Space Nine?</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:13:36.634 --> 00:13:38.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just telling you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what the translation said.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:13:38.754 --> 00:13:40.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did not say I believed it.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:13:40.233 --> 00:13:41.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm not worried.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:13:41.593 --> 00:13:43.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you look hard enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll find a Bajoran prophecy</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:13:43.752 --> 00:13:44.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for just about anything.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:13:44.712 --> 00:13:47.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ancient texts are a tangle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of vague contradictions.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:13:47.551 --> 00:13:49.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, this one is anything but vague</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:13:49.470 --> 00:13:52.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and Bajoran prophecies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have an odd way of coming true.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:13:52.109 --> 00:13:53.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't say you believe in this stuff, too?</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:13:53.749 --> 00:13:55.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo believes in preparing for the worst.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:13:55.828 --> 00:13:56.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>True.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:13:56.908 --> 00:13:58.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's as bad as the Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:13:59.827 --> 00:14:02.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Business hasn't been this slow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since the Dominion was here.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:14:03.986 --> 00:14:06.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I feel I have a civic duty</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:14:06.345 --> 00:14:08.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to do something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about all this doom and gloom</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:14:08.465 --> 00:14:10.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>which is why I want to tell you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I've extended happy hour.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:14:10.904 --> 00:14:12.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Extended it?</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:14:12.983 --> 00:14:15.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From now on, every hour is happy hour...</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:14:16.303 --> 00:14:17.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>at least until business picks up.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:14:18.221 --> 00:14:19.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eat, drink, and be merry.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:19.501 --> 00:14:21.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For tomorrow, we die.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:22.461 --> 00:14:25.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what does the Captain say about this?</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:14:25.340 --> 00:14:26.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is reserving judgment</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:26.819 --> 00:14:28.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>until the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has finished the translation.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:28.818 --> 00:14:31.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who knows? The rest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the tablet probably says</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:14:31.258 --> 00:14:33.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Go to Quark's. It's happy hour."</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:33.137 --> 00:14:34.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like the way you think, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:14:34.537 --> 00:14:37.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, this is ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing's going to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:14:37.296 --> 00:14:39.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Someday, we're all going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to look back on this and laugh.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:14:40.215 --> 00:14:42.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:14:42.974 --> 00:14:44.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: What was that?</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:14:56.290 --> 00:14:58.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:15:00.689 --> 00:15:02.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did that prophecy go again?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:15:07.767 --> 00:15:09.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: You don't have to do this, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:15:09.647 --> 00:15:11.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Don't have to do what?</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:15:11.686 --> 00:15:14.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sit here, watch me eat.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:15:14.685 --> 00:15:17.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't mind.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>In fact, I rather enjoy it.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:15:17.964 --> 00:15:19.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You eat with such gusto...</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:15:21.123 --> 00:15:22.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>most of the time.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:15:22.842 --> 00:15:24.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not today.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:15:27.161 --> 00:15:29.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just wish that we knew more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the Reckoning.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:15:29.440 --> 00:15:32.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would give us a better idea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of what the Prophets want from us.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:15:33.559 --> 00:15:36.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems to me that, if the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:36.958 --> 00:15:39.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>want the Bajoran people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to follow a given path</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:39.317 --> 00:15:42.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they should provide</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more specific directions.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:43.196 --> 00:15:44.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't work like that.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:15:44.635 --> 00:15:46.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe it should.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:15:46.475 --> 00:15:48.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Kai would say that you lack faith.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:15:50.115 --> 00:15:51.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you would agree.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:15:52.794 --> 00:15:55.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just don't know how people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make it through the day without it.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:15:56.912 --> 00:15:58.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We manage.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:15:59.272 --> 00:16:01.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, I do have faith in some things.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:16:01.751 --> 00:16:03.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling ) Such as?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:16:03.470 --> 00:16:04.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:16:08.109 --> 00:16:09.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll try not to disappoint you.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:16:14.275 --> 00:16:16.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No doubt you've heard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the latest news from Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:16:17.146 --> 00:16:19.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>About the flooding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Rakantha Province, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:16:21.265 --> 00:16:25.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was also an earthquake</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Kendra Valley last night.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:16:25.663 --> 00:16:28.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This morning, a tornado struck Tamulna.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:29.626 --> 00:16:31.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our sensors indicate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that Bajor has been affected</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:31.661 --> 00:16:33.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>by the instability of the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:33.341 --> 00:16:34.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How comforting.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:16:34.941 --> 00:16:37.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, do your sensors</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have an explanation</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:16:37.740 --> 00:16:39.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for the instability itself?</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:16:40.939 --> 00:16:42.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:16:42.419 --> 00:16:43.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I'll give you one.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:16:45.257 --> 00:16:49.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've angered the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by taking the tablet from Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:16:49.137 --> 00:16:51.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As the spiritual leader</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Bajoran people</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:16:51.576 --> 00:16:53.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you to return it.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:16:54.255 --> 00:16:56.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And as the Emissary of the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:16:56.135 --> 00:16:58.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will ask you to give me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more time to study it.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:16:58.774 --> 00:17:00.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe it is the will of the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:17:01.173 --> 00:17:02.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I disagree.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:17:02.932 --> 00:17:05.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is a formal request</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the First Minister</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:05.492 --> 00:17:08.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for you to turn over the relic to me.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:08.491 --> 00:17:11.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must have been very persuasive.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:11.210 --> 00:17:14.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the first time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you and Shakaar have agreed on anything.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:15.568 --> 00:17:18.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you deny his request, I promise you</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:18.608 --> 00:17:22.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it will damage relations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between Bajor and the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:29.205 --> 00:17:30.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The tablet...</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:31.764 --> 00:17:34.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be on its way to Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the morning transport.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:17:34.443 --> 00:17:35.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( places padd on desk )</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:17:40.421 --> 00:17:41.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As will I.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:17:48.559 --> 00:17:51.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're sending it back?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And I was just starting to have fun.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:17:51.758 --> 00:17:55.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not letting you off the hook, old man.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I need these inscriptions translated.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:17:55.957 --> 00:17:58.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can work off the holo-recordings</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I took yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:17:58.956 --> 00:18:00.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you made any more progress?</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:18:01.754 --> 00:18:02.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good news or bad?</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:18:02.874 --> 00:18:04.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On what?</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:18:04.195 --> 00:18:05.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On what this ideogram means.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:18:05.954 --> 00:18:07.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer has given me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>two possibilities.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:18:07.873 --> 00:18:08.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are?</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:09.472 --> 00:18:10.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>During the Reckoning</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:10.913 --> 00:18:12.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Bajorans will either "suffer horribly"</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:18:13.318 --> 00:18:14.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or "eat fruit."</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:18:16.631 --> 00:18:17.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Eat fruit"?</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:18:19.429 --> 00:18:22.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Given the tone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the rest of the inscriptions</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:18:23.428 --> 00:18:24.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would bet on horrible suffering.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:18:25.627 --> 00:18:26.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What else do you have?</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:18:27.187 --> 00:18:29.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll love this. It's about you.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:18:30.906 --> 00:18:34.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Once the Reckoning begins,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Emissary will..."</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:18:35.225 --> 00:18:36.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:18:36.304 --> 00:18:37.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping you could tell me.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:18:38.464 --> 00:18:40.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, the rest of the</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>inscription's damaged.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:18:40.703 --> 00:18:42.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that figures.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:18:42.223 --> 00:18:44.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:18:44.382 --> 00:18:46.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I wish the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would stop doing that.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:18:46.542 --> 00:18:48.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do I. Keep at it, old man.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:18:48.461 --> 00:18:49.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just do me one favor.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:18:49.981 --> 00:18:53.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you talk to the Prophets again</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ask for a dictionary...</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:18:54.219 --> 00:18:55.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>please.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:18:55.579 --> 00:18:57.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see what I can do.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:18:57.259 --> 00:18:58.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:19:04.696 --> 00:19:07.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, I have a message for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from General Martok.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:19:07.695 --> 00:19:08.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:19:08.695 --> 00:19:10.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's dispatched</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three Klingon attack cruisers</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:19:10.854 --> 00:19:13.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to bolster the defense perimeter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the Dorala system.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:19:13.653 --> 00:19:17.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good. I just hope they can hold out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until Starfleet sends in reinforcements.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:19:17.852 --> 00:19:20.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons will hold out.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Martok will see to it.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:19:24.210 --> 00:19:25.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Long day?</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:19:25.890 --> 00:19:27.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They seem to get longer.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:19:28.129 --> 00:19:29.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll feel better in the morning...</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:19:30.528 --> 00:19:32.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>once the Kai is off the station.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:19:32.878 --> 00:19:33.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:19:34.474 --> 00:19:36.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She may be the spiritual leader</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of millions of Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:19:36.847 --> 00:19:39.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but she is not an easy woman to like.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:19:39.166 --> 00:19:42.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if it's any comfort</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think she likes you, either.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:19:42.205 --> 00:19:43.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've known that for a while.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:19:43.924 --> 00:19:45.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I should have consulted her</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:19:45.444 --> 00:19:47.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>before I brought the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>up to the station.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:19:47.803 --> 00:19:49.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She would have tried to stop you.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:19:49.563 --> 00:19:51.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah... that's why I didn't ask her.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:19:52.202 --> 00:19:53.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a way, I feel sorry for her.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:19:53.961 --> 00:19:57.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She spends her whole life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in service to the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:19:57.320 --> 00:20:01.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then one day, after years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of self-sacrifice and commitment</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:20:01.359 --> 00:20:03.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>she gets her reward. She's elected Kai.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:20:04.382 --> 00:20:06.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Should've been the greatest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>moment of her life.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:20:08.556 --> 00:20:11.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But my being the Emissary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>spoiled it for her.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:20:11.715 --> 00:20:14.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, the Kai's always been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the spiritual leader of Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:20:14.715 --> 00:20:16.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Winn has to share that role with you</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:20:16.994 --> 00:20:18.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to make matters worse</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:20:18.594 --> 00:20:20.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you're an outsider, a non-Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:20:20.353 --> 00:20:22.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she can never forgive you for.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:20:22.432 --> 00:20:25.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's why she made</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>such an issue of the whole thing.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:20:25.632 --> 00:20:27.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, she's jealous of you</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:20:27.351 --> 00:20:30.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and of your relationship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:20:31.190 --> 00:20:32.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a little envious myself.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:20:32.790 --> 00:20:34.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:20:34.789 --> 00:20:37.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You speak with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:20:37.148 --> 00:20:38.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They listen to you.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:20:38.548 --> 00:20:39.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's...</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:20:39.827 --> 00:20:41.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that's a rare gift.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:20:41.987 --> 00:20:43.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Certainly nothing I asked for.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:20:43.907 --> 00:20:47.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's why I don't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>resent you, but the Kai does.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:20:50.384 --> 00:20:52.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll keep that in mind.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:21:05.100 --> 00:21:06.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, Eminence?</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:21:08.299 --> 00:21:09.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you say that, child?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:21:10.187 --> 00:21:11.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seem troubled.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:21:11.178 --> 00:21:12.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:21:12.737 --> 00:21:14.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am quite relieved</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:21:14.137 --> 00:21:16.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Emissary has decided</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to do the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:21:17.569 --> 00:21:18.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you didn't leave him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>much choice, did you?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:21:19.855 --> 00:21:23.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I enjoyed forcing his hand.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:21:24.215 --> 00:21:26.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assure you, I did not.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:21:26.974 --> 00:21:30.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish the situation had been resolved</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more amicably.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:21:30.932 --> 00:21:33.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps the next time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have a disagreement</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:21:33.291 --> 00:21:35.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'll consider my wishes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more thoughtfully.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:21:35.610 --> 00:21:36.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The next time?</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:21:36.691 --> 00:21:38.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're anticipating more disagreements?</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:21:40.250 --> 00:21:43.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I merely meant to express</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my hope that, in the future</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:21:43.249 --> 00:21:45.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we can work together</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the good of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:21:45.728 --> 00:21:46.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:21:46.767 --> 00:21:49.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After all, you are on the same side,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aren't you?</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:21:49.567 --> 00:21:50.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Naturally.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:21:51.406 --> 00:21:53.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We both serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:21:53.445 --> 00:21:55.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is no higher calling.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:21:59.446 --> 00:22:01.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:22:04.425 --> 00:22:05.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:22:05.641 --> 00:22:06.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:22:06.601 --> 00:22:07.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:22:09.415 --> 00:22:09.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake-o.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:22:17.787 --> 00:22:18.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're up late.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:22:18.758 --> 00:22:20.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, so are you.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:22:20.397 --> 00:22:21.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's on your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:22:22.757 --> 00:22:24.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know. I guess I just wanted to see</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you're all right.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:22:26.755 --> 00:22:27.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:22:28.115 --> 00:22:30.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Since when did you become a worrier?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:22:32.154 --> 00:22:33.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:22:34.274 --> 00:22:36.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's this Emissary stuff.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:22:36.672 --> 00:22:38.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It scares me a little.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:22:45.110 --> 00:22:46.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Twice now...</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:22:46.590 --> 00:22:48.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>twice in one year...</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:22:49.189 --> 00:22:51.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Bashir's called me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>down to the Infirmary</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:22:51.468 --> 00:22:53.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to tell me something was wrong with you</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:22:53.947 --> 00:22:55.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there you were</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:22:56.226 --> 00:22:59.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lying unconscious on a bio-bed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>having visions or something.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:23:01.305 --> 00:23:02.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And there...</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:23:02.424 --> 00:23:04.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all I could do was just stand there</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:23:05.624 --> 00:23:06.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and, and wonder...</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:23:07.903 --> 00:23:09.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>if you were ever going to wake up.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:23:12.462 --> 00:23:14.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know it hasn't been easy, Jake.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:23:15.461 --> 00:23:17.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want it to happen again.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:23:21.199 --> 00:23:24.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I didn't ask</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be the Emissary...</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:23:26.658 --> 00:23:30.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, for better or worse,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's what I am...</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:23:33.336 --> 00:23:34.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>except for being your dad.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:24:18.562 --> 00:24:23.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do you always have to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so damned mysterious?</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:24:25.400 --> 00:24:26.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Answer me.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:24:28.439 --> 00:24:30.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am tired of your riddles!</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:24:31.998 --> 00:24:35.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you need me to do, say so!</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:24:39.676 --> 00:24:40.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:25:07.907 --> 00:25:09.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me guess.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:25:09.786 --> 00:25:12.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You accidentally knocked it over.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:25:12.866 --> 00:25:13.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:25:14.253 --> 00:25:15.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think so.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:25:15.265 --> 00:25:17.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what did happen?</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:25:18.504 --> 00:25:21.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just had this uncontrollable urge</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:25:21.663 --> 00:25:23.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to smash the tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:25:23.743 --> 00:25:25.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I get those urges all the time.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:25:26.101 --> 00:25:28.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, I never act on them.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:25:30.141 --> 00:25:33.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not reading</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any residual energy signatures.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:25:33.340 --> 00:25:36.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's impossible.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Check the station's internal sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:25:38.618 --> 00:25:39.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:25:39.817 --> 00:25:41.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I tell you, I saw something.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:25:41.537 --> 00:25:42.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We believe you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:25:42.857 --> 00:25:45.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, please, Constable, don't patronize me.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:25:49.375 --> 00:25:50.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sisko to Ops. Report.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:25:50.894 --> 00:25:53.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We just experienced</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a station-wide power drain.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:25:53.373 --> 00:25:54.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're attempting to determine the source.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:25:55.173 --> 00:25:56.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep me informed.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:25:56.173 --> 00:25:57.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Aye, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

455
00:25:57.453 --> 00:26:02.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's possible the power drain is related</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to this energy discharge you saw.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:26:03.771 --> 00:26:05.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm starting to think the same thing.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:26:07.689 --> 00:26:10.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, you're not getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another urge, are you?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:26:11.528 --> 00:26:12.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:26:15.567 --> 00:26:17.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've done what I needed to do.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:26:18.966 --> 00:26:21.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know this might sound strange</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:26:22.325 --> 00:26:25.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I think the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted me to shatter the tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:26:25.244 --> 00:26:27.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try explaining that to Kai Winn.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:26:28.203 --> 00:26:30.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe that you'd be so petty</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:26:30.682 --> 00:26:34.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as to destroy the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>rather than turn it over to me.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:26:34.121 --> 00:26:35.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not why I did it.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:26:36.481 --> 00:26:39.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the Prophets wanted you</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:26:39.759 --> 00:26:43.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy a priceless piece</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Bajor's history?</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:26:43.639 --> 00:26:45.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's exactly what you have to believe.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:26:46.398 --> 00:26:48.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And why would they do that?</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:26:48.317 --> 00:26:50.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I had an answer for you.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:26:50.637 --> 00:26:52.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm sure you'll</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>come up with something.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:26:55.715 --> 00:26:58.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and I haven't always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seen things eye to eye</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:26:58.994 --> 00:27:00.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we have one thing in common--</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:27:00.633 --> 00:27:03.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we both believe that the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have a plan for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:27:03.353 --> 00:27:06.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, sometimes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's not easy to see the path</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:27:06.471 --> 00:27:07.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>they've laid out for us.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:27:08.831 --> 00:27:12.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right now, I don't know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what they want from me</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:27:12.990 --> 00:27:15.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm willing to take a leap of faith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and trust that they're guiding me</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:27:15.869 --> 00:27:18.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm asking you to</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>take that leap with me.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:27:18.548 --> 00:27:21.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a leap of faith, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:27:21.707 --> 00:27:24.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets have made it quite clear.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:27:24.586 --> 00:27:28.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two-thirds of the Rakantha wheat harvest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have been destroyed by floods.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:27:28.545 --> 00:27:30.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Earthquakes have devastated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kendra Province</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:27:31.648 --> 00:27:32.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>leaving hundreds homeless.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:27:33.623 --> 00:27:36.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajorans are suffering because of you.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:27:36.383 --> 00:27:39.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're paying the price</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for your act of sacrilege.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:27:42.221 --> 00:27:44.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Captain Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

488
00:27:44.261 --> 00:27:45.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:27:45.580 --> 00:27:47.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> You'd better come down</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Promenade, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

490
00:27:47.939 --> 00:27:49.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there a problem?</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:27:49.139 --> 00:27:50.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> I'll let you be the judge of that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:28:02.735 --> 00:28:05.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think we've found the source</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the power fluctuations.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:28:06.545 --> 00:28:08.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I tried to talk to her,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she ignored me.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:28:14.931 --> 00:28:16.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( wind whistling )</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:28:16.771 --> 00:28:18.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( glass exploding )</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:28:32.206 --> 00:28:35.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( voice reverberating) You...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:28:36.844 --> 00:28:38.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep your hands off your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:28:39.442 --> 00:28:40.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a Prophet.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:28:41.843 --> 00:28:43.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why have you taken this woman's body?</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:28:44.722 --> 00:28:46.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This vessel is willing.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:28:48.401 --> 00:28:49.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Reckoning...</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:28:50.920 --> 00:28:51.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it is time.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:28:59.398 --> 00:29:01.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The Reckoning... what is it?</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:29:01.677 --> 00:29:02.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The end...</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:29:03.637 --> 00:29:04.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:29:04.996 --> 00:29:06.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:29:08.915 --> 00:29:10.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I await Kosst Amojan.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:29:10.954 --> 00:29:12.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Evil One.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:29:13.313 --> 00:29:16.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Pah-wraith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>banished from the Celestial Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:29:17.753 --> 00:29:21.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying a Pah-wraith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will take corporeal form as well?</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:29:21.271 --> 00:29:22.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The battle will be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:29:23.150 --> 00:29:25.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This battle... is it to be fought here?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:29:25.790 --> 00:29:27.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor will be reborn.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:29:28.749 --> 00:29:30.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shabren's Fifth Prophecy--</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:29:31.788 --> 00:29:33.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Rebirth.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:29:33.108 --> 00:29:36.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the Evil One is destroyed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it will bring a thousand years of peace--</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:29:37.746 --> 00:29:40.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Golden Age of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:29:41.945 --> 00:29:43.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it is destroyed?</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:29:45.824 --> 00:29:47.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who will prevail is not known.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:29:47.863 --> 00:29:49.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want from me?</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:29:49.943 --> 00:29:52.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Am I supposed to help you in some way?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:29:52.182 --> 00:29:55.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko has completed his task.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:29:59.220 --> 00:30:01.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive my blindness.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:30:04.588 --> 00:30:05.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prophet, hear me.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:30:06.185 --> 00:30:07.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am the Kai of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:30:08.177 --> 00:30:12.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I offer myself to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as your humble servant.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:30:12.656 --> 00:30:14.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I await their vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:30:15.455 --> 00:30:16.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Speak to me.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:30:16.735 --> 00:30:18.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me what I should do.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:30:28.931 --> 00:30:30.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're evacuating.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:30:31.531 --> 00:30:32.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't be serious.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:30:33.103 --> 00:30:35.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This battle could destroy the station.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:30:35.249 --> 00:30:36.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then don't let it be fought here.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:30:37.328 --> 00:30:38.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have any choice.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:30:38.888 --> 00:30:40.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, you do.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:30:40.487 --> 00:30:43.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can flood the Promenade</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with chroniton radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:30:43.246 --> 00:30:45.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you suggesting that we kill a Prophet?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:30:45.646 --> 00:30:46.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:30:46.645 --> 00:30:48.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: You don't have to.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:30:48.285 --> 00:30:50.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you ramp up the chroniton levels slowly</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:30:50.924 --> 00:30:52.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you'll give the wormhole alien</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a chance to leave</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:30:52.523 --> 00:30:54.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kira's body without getting hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:30:54.483 --> 00:30:56.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: We have everything rigged</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and ready to go.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:30:56.723 --> 00:30:57.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just say the word.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:31:02.281 --> 00:31:03.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:31:03.640 --> 00:31:04.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:31:06.119 --> 00:31:09.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deep Space Nine is critical</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the defense of the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:31:09.118 --> 00:31:10.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We cannot risk destroying it.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:31:10.918 --> 00:31:13.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Dominion fleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was about to come through the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:31:14.357 --> 00:31:16.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked the Prophets for their help.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:31:16.116 --> 00:31:17.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:31:17.597 --> 00:31:19.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now they're asking for my help.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:31:20.362 --> 00:31:22.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They need to fight this battle here, now.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:31:22.395 --> 00:31:24.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to jeopardize my crew</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:31:25.834 --> 00:31:28.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm not going to stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the way of the Prophets, either.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:31:28.713 --> 00:31:30.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if the Prophets lose?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:31:30.353 --> 00:31:32.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you willing to sacrifice Kira?</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:31:32.512 --> 00:31:35.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophet said she was willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:31:35.591 --> 00:31:36.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:31:36.911 --> 00:31:37.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I do.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:31:41.229 --> 00:31:44.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know how important</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>her faith is to her and...</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:31:44.348 --> 00:31:47.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no doubt that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she would allow the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:31:47.147 --> 00:31:49.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to use her as their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:31:52.626 --> 00:31:55.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll notify Starfleet that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're abandoning the station.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:31:57.185 --> 00:31:58.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Begin the evacuation immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:32:10.941 --> 00:32:13.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Hurry along, now. Hurry along.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:32:13.780 --> 00:32:15.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is this transport full?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-There's room.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:32:15.379 --> 00:32:17.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to check the</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Promenade for stragglers.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:32:17.779 --> 00:32:21.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo, you should've helped us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>persuade the Captain to end this.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:32:21.937 --> 00:32:23.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to respect Kira's wishes.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:32:24.217 --> 00:32:26.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it were Dax, I am not sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I could've done the same.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:32:26.776 --> 00:32:29.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, just be grateful</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you didn't have to make that choice.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:32:30.694 --> 00:32:33.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For your sake, I hope</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets are victorious.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:32:33.494 --> 00:32:36.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They will be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if Kira has anything to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:32:38.652 --> 00:32:39.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:32:42.251 --> 00:32:43.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Report.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:32:43.411 --> 00:32:45.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We expect to be down to a skeleton crew</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>within the hour.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:32:45.769 --> 00:32:46.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very well.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:32:46.889 --> 00:32:48.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did Starfleet have to say?</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:32:48.529 --> 00:32:49.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I managed to convince them</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:32:49.969 --> 00:32:52.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that we couldn't afford</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to defy the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:32:52.881 --> 00:32:53.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: They are the only thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's keeping the Dominion</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:32:53.727 --> 00:32:55.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:32:55.447 --> 00:32:58.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only problem is, there's no guarantee</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets will win this battle.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:32:58.886 --> 00:33:00.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

586
00:33:00.205 --> 00:33:01.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Constable.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:33:01.605 --> 00:33:02.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Captain, there's a group of Bajorans</i></c.bg_transparent>

588
00:33:03.447 --> 00:33:05.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>on the Promenade</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>who are refusing to leave.</i></c.bg_transparent>

589
00:33:07.443 --> 00:33:12.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WINN:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Tera dak embah</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ihsehelm ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

590
00:33:12.762 --> 00:33:14.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ALL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>de-ram ta-meen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

591
00:33:16.521 --> 00:33:18.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tera dak ihsehelm</i></c.bg_transparent>

592
00:33:18.560 --> 00:33:19.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

593
00:33:20.560 --> 00:33:22.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ALL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>de-ram ta-meen...</i></c.bg_transparent>

594
00:33:22.199 --> 00:33:24.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last transports are standing by.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:33:24.839 --> 00:33:28.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WINN:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Tera dak ihsehelm</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

596
00:33:28.837 --> 00:33:29.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eminence.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:33:29.877 --> 00:33:31.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>...ta-meen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

598
00:33:33.476 --> 00:33:34.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:33:34.595 --> 00:33:35.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>These people have to go.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:33:37.275 --> 00:33:39.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're offering prayers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Prophets' victory.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:33:40.233 --> 00:33:42.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will hear your prayers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wherever you are.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:33:42.713 --> 00:33:44.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It isn't safe here.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:33:45.552 --> 00:33:47.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why are you still here, Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:33:48.311 --> 00:33:50.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophet told you your task was done.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:33:51.303 --> 00:33:52.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am Captain of this station</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:33:52.829 --> 00:33:55.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I will do everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my power to save it.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:33:55.309 --> 00:33:57.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, are you going to</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tell these people to go</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:33:58.283 --> 00:33:59.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or shall I?</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:34:04.466 --> 00:34:05.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My children</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:34:05.786 --> 00:34:07.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets have heard your prayers.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:34:07.746 --> 00:34:09.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must go.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:34:13.224 --> 00:34:14.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take them to the transports.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:34:17.262 --> 00:34:18.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, this way.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:34:18.862 --> 00:34:21.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:34:21.182 --> 00:34:23.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks to you the Prophets'</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>victory is at hand.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:34:23.860 --> 00:34:25.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you're right.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:34:25.780 --> 00:34:27.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is your faith, Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:34:27.979 --> 00:34:30.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't think the Evil One</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be victorious, do you?</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:34:32.138 --> 00:34:35.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rest assured, the Golden Age is upon us.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:34:36.257 --> 00:34:39.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets and the people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be as one.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:34:40.562 --> 00:34:41.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:34:41.176 --> 00:34:44.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There will be no need for vedeks or kais</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:34:44.895 --> 00:34:46.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or even Emissaries.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:34:49.813 --> 00:34:52.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kosst Amojan has chosen its vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:35:04.878 --> 00:35:05.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let it begin.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:35:13.605 --> 00:35:15.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leave my son and take me instead!</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:35:17.884 --> 00:35:20.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your Emissary offers himself to us.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:35:21.364 --> 00:35:22.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His faith wavers.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:35:24.162 --> 00:35:25.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:35:35.519 --> 00:35:37.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:36:01.791 --> 00:36:03.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary, we must go.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:36:14.667 --> 00:36:16.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, Worf is standing by in Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:36:16.627 --> 00:36:19.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He can trigger the chroniton generator</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at your command.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:36:19.385 --> 00:36:20.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can still end this, Ben.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:36:20.546 --> 00:36:21.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I've got to play this thing out.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:36:22.657 --> 00:36:23.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is your son out there.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:36:23.664 --> 00:36:26.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you think I know that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will protect him.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:36:26.663 --> 00:36:27.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're trying to kill him.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:36:28.636 --> 00:36:30.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. They're trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy the Pah-wraith.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:36:30.622 --> 00:36:33.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will not let</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anything happen to him.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:36:33.142 --> 00:36:34.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know that?</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:36:34.381 --> 00:36:35.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:36:37.620 --> 00:36:38.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to get out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:36:38.820 --> 00:36:40.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to the sensors,</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:36:40.180 --> 00:36:43.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the energy building between them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could explode at any second.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:36:43.339 --> 00:36:44.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to leave Jake here.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:36:46.738 --> 00:36:48.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We must go, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:36:48.537 --> 00:36:49.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin...</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:36:49.577 --> 00:36:52.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get out of here!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get off the station, both of you!</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:36:52.256 --> 00:36:53.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's an order!</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:36:53.336 --> 00:36:54.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come, child. We must go.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:37:03.173 --> 00:37:04.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax to Worf.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:37:07.771 --> 00:37:08.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:37:08.851 --> 00:37:10.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Meet me at Airlock Eight. We're leaving.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:37:14.809 --> 00:37:16.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on ahead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Airlock Eight is down to the right.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:37:17.968 --> 00:37:20.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This way. Move quickly.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:37:20.368 --> 00:37:22.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go. Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:37:22.407 --> 00:37:23.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hurry up.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:37:23.527 --> 00:37:25.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's okay, it's okay.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:37:25.686 --> 00:37:27.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think the transport is down here.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:37:51.438 --> 00:37:53.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:37:54.277 --> 00:37:57.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chroniton levels at 37% and rising.</i></c.bg_transparent>

663
00:37:59.156 --> 00:38:01.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May the Prophets forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:38:24.188 --> 00:38:25.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake...</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:38:33.745 --> 00:38:35.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's Log, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

666
00:38:35.905 --> 00:38:39.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The station's population</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>has returned</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and repairs are underway.</i></c.bg_transparent>

667
00:38:40.246 --> 00:38:42.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Major Kira has recovered</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>from her experience...</i></c.bg_transparent>

668
00:38:42.903 --> 00:38:45.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>but my son is still</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>in the Infirmary.</i></c.bg_transparent>

669
00:38:47.102 --> 00:38:48.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:38:48.141 --> 00:38:50.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be, uh, laid up for a few days</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he'll be all right.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:38:51.101 --> 00:38:52.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I see him?</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:38:52.101 --> 00:38:52.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:39:00.657 --> 00:39:01.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake...</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:39:04.896 --> 00:39:05.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dad.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:39:06.456 --> 00:39:07.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:39:08.735 --> 00:39:10.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Could be worse.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:39:12.546 --> 00:39:13.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be up and about in no time.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:39:17.133 --> 00:39:19.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what to say.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:39:20.251 --> 00:39:22.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Say you're happy to see me.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:39:23.131 --> 00:39:24.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know I am.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:39:26.850 --> 00:39:28.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I...</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:39:30.569 --> 00:39:32.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to explain what happened...</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:39:34.607 --> 00:39:36.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm not sure that I can.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:39:38.406 --> 00:39:39.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't have to explain.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:39:41.286 --> 00:39:43.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Pah-wraith was inside me</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:39:44.484 --> 00:39:46.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could feel its hatred</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:39:47.836 --> 00:39:50.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I knew that no matter what</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:39:50.962 --> 00:39:52.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it couldn't be allowed to win...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:39:55.815 --> 00:39:56.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>even if it meant I had to die.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:39:59.839 --> 00:40:01.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:40:14.636 --> 00:40:16.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How was the prayer service?</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:40:16.275 --> 00:40:18.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To tell you the truth</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't pay that much attention.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:40:18.794 --> 00:40:21.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still trying to make sense</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of everything that happened.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:40:21.273 --> 00:40:25.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, of all the people on this station</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets chose me.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:40:25.672 --> 00:40:29.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure I know why</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve that honor.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:40:29.511 --> 00:40:32.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps that's why you were chosen.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have faith and humility.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:40:32.150 --> 00:40:34.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I heard that you told the Captain</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:40:34.350 --> 00:40:36.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that I was willing to give my life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:40:37.909 --> 00:40:40.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate that you respect my beliefs.</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:40:41.348 --> 00:40:45.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just the same, I wouldn't have minded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if the Prophets had chosen someone else.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:40:48.385 --> 00:40:49.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to go.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:40:49.785 --> 00:40:52.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll drop by Security</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after I take the Kai to her shuttle.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:41:02.181 --> 00:41:04.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary couldn't escort me himself?</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:41:05.221 --> 00:41:06.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's with his son.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:41:06.700 --> 00:41:08.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would think he'd want to thank me.</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:41:08.859 --> 00:41:10.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For what?</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:41:10.659 --> 00:41:13.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I prevented the destruction</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this station.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:41:13.617 --> 00:41:17.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saved the Emissary's life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the life of his son.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:41:17.616 --> 00:41:19.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't pretend you did it for the Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:41:20.536 --> 00:41:22.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did it for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:41:22.375 --> 00:41:25.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you haven't heard,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the floodwaters have receded</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:41:25.574 --> 00:41:27.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the earthquakes have stopped.</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:41:27.294 --> 00:41:29.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you're going to take credit for that?</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:41:30.612 --> 00:41:33.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it as a sign I did the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

715
00:41:33.292 --> 00:41:35.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You defied the will of the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

716
00:41:35.252 --> 00:41:36.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and you did it</c.bg_transparent>

717
00:41:36.571 --> 00:41:40.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because you couldn't stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the fact that a human, an infidel,</c.bg_transparent>

718
00:41:41.900 --> 00:41:42.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>had a stronger faith than you.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:41:43.368 --> 00:41:45.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary was willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to sacrifice his own son</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:41:45.888 --> 00:41:47.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

721
00:41:47.968 --> 00:41:50.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My faith is as pure as the Emissary's.</c.bg_transparent>

722
00:41:52.639 --> 00:41:55.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you're confusing faith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with ambition.</c.bg_transparent>

723
00:41:55.725 --> 00:41:59.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not confusing anything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>child, you are.</c.bg_transparent>

724
00:41:59.764 --> 00:42:02.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets chose you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

725
00:42:02.843 --> 00:42:05.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't mean you can speak for them.</c.bg_transparent>

726
00:42:06.828 --> 00:42:09.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because of your interference,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Reckoning was stopped.</c.bg_transparent>

727
00:42:09.441 --> 00:42:11.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The evil still exists.</c.bg_transparent>

728
00:42:12.160 --> 00:42:16.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm not sure if even the Prophets know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what that will mean for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

